<item>
            <title>[LU-5384] Static analysis issues in lfsck</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5384</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Array &apos;name&apos; of size 8 may use index value(s) 8..11&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/lfsck/lfsck_lib.c&lt;/tt&gt;:700: Array &apos;name&apos; size is 8.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/lfsck/lfsck_lib.c&lt;/tt&gt;:707: Length of format string &quot;MDT%04x&quot; is 11.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="25672">LU-5384</key>
            <summary>Static analysis issues in lfsck</summary>
